name: Pam Kitty Darling Set pre-order
description:
This Darling Set has pretty posies in bright pinks, reds, yellows and blues on a white background covered with pale pink spots, from the new Pam Kitty range. This style has a white embroidered collar and straps in hot pink spot that can be tied as a halter neck or threaded through loops on the back waist band and tied in a bow. It also has three ruffles across the back and a pretty lavender satin bow. This style has a snap crotch for easy nappy change.
Please allow up to 2 weeks for your order to be completed.

name: Sunshine Roses Ruffle Shorts Set pre-order
description:
This set includes the ruffle shorts made from the gorgeous Tanya Whelan fabric Sunshine Roses. There are three ruffles across the back made from pink spots, pretty white lace and the beautiful pastel roses of Sunshine Roses.
The top is made using the Fresh Designs pattern and has the white embroidered collar that was used on the Darling Playsuit.
I can make either size 1, 2, 3 or 4. Please let me know what size you would like. 
Please allow up to 2 weeks for your order to be completed.
